sorcer.util.bdb.objects
Class MarshalledData

java.lang.Object
  sorcer.util.bdb.objects.MarshalledData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Identifiable
public class MarshalledData
extends Object
implements Serializable, Identifiable

A MarshalledData serves as the data in the key/data pair for multiple entities.

The MarshalledData class is used both as the storage entry for the data as well as the object binding to the value. Because it is used directly as storage data using serial format, it must be Serializable.

Mike Sobolewski
